<Box component="main" sx={{ flexGrow: 1, p: 3, marginTop: showAppBar ? '64px' : '0px' }}>
<Grid container spacing={2}>
  <Grid item xs={12}>
    <Paper>
      {children}
      {window.location.pathname === '/topstocks' && renderTopStocks()}
    </Paper>
  </Grid>
</Grid>
</Box>
